{"id":233710,"type":6,"name":"Dan Cruickshank Adventures in Architecture","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/08/26/233710_id3Z1.jpg","summary":"主持人丹·克鲁克山克周游世界，遍访各式建筑，展示这些建筑是如何体现我们人类的意愿、天赋和信念。在每期节目中，世界各地的建筑物被戏剧性的罗列在一起，观众将发现，尽管建筑风格迥异，它们之间竟有着意想不到的联系。从俄罗斯西北边陲的基日岛的木结构教堂，到埃及西奈的圣凯瑟琳修道院，本系列是一段汇聚了众多不朽建筑、具有里程碑意义的旅程。《漫游世界建筑群》不仅能丰富观众的建筑学知识，更为观众讲述了世界建筑的动人故事。","info":"<li><span>中文名: </span>漫游世界建筑群</li><li><span>别名: </span>BBC 漫游世界建筑群</li><li><span>集数: </span>8</li><li><span>开始: </span>2008-04-12</li><li><span>国家/地区: </span>英国</li><li><span>语言: </span>英語</li><li><span>imdb_id: </span>tt1045263</li>","eps":[{"id":765860,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/765860","type":0,"sort":1,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":765861,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/765861","type":0,"sort":2,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":765862,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/765862","type":0,"sort":3,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":765863,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/765863","type":0,"sort":4,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":765864,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/765864","type":0,"sort":5,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":765865,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/765865","type":0,"sort":6,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":765866,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/765866","type":0,"sort":7,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":765867,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/765867","type":0,"sort":8,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"}]}